ComicInfo.Summary:
The Forest of Grinning Teeth
The Dark Cheshire is put on trial for his involvement with the Queens of Wonderland and his recurrent bloody excursions to Earth. By decree of the Lord Cheshire of the Forest of Grinning Teeth, he is forced into a game of cat-and-mouse. With Dark Cheshire's very existence on the line, Calie must face the Lord Cheshire and the pride that serves him.
